

## **2. Maxima & Minima**
### **Key Concepts:**
- **Critical points** (First & Second Derivative Tests)  
- **Absolute vs. Local Extrema**  
- **Optimization problems** (Applied in Engineering)  
- **Concavity & Inflection Points**  

